                        <interp inst="t18440408-name-107" type="given" value="MARY"></interp>MARY WATSON</persName>
                  </hi>. I am the wife of Abraham Watson, who keeps the Britannia public-house, Limehouse. Mr. Mann supplied us with meat, which I was in the habit of paying for as it was delivered—on the 9th of March, I paid the prisoner 1<hi rend="italic">l</hi>. 10<hi rend="italic">s</hi>. 4<hi rend="italic">d</hi>. for his master—he receipted this bill, "Paid E. Jones," in my presence.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
